---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Resources">
	<section class="page-header">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>Fertility Resources</h1>
			<p>Organizations, support groups, financial assistance, and educational materials.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="content-container">
		<h2>Professional Organizations</h2>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>ASRM - American Society for Reproductive Medicine</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.asrm.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">asrm.org</a></p>
			<p>Professional organization for fertility specialists. Offers patient resources, fact sheets, and guidelines.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>SART - Society for Assisted Reproductive Technology</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.sart.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">sart.org</a></p>
			<p>Search clinic success rates, find accredited clinics, and access patient resources.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>RESOLVE: The National Infertility Association</h3>
			<p><a href="https://resolve.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">resolve.org</a></p>
			<p>Patient advocacy organization offering support groups, educational events, and insurance advocacy resources.</p>
		</div>

		<h2>Finding a Clinic</h2>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>SART Clinic Finder</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.sart.org/patients/find-a-clinic/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">sart.org/patients/find-a-clinic</a></p>
			<p>Search for fertility clinics by location and compare CDC-reported success rates.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>CDC ART Success Rates</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.cdc.gov/art/artdata/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cdc.gov/art</a></p>
			<p>Official CDC data on clinic success rates. Use with caution - rates reflect patient population, not just clinic quality.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="info-box">
			<strong>Comparing Clinics:</strong> Don't choose a clinic based on success rates alone. Consider patient reviews, doctor-patient ratio, location, cost, and whether they accept your insurance.
		</div>

		<h2>Financial Assistance</h2>

		<h3>Grants and Scholarships</h3>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>Baby Quest Foundation</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.babyquestfoundation.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">babyquestfoundation.org</a></p>
			<p>Grants up to $16,000 for IVF, gestational surrogacy, egg/sperm donation.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>The Cade Foundation</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.cadefoundation.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">cadefoundation.org</a></p>
			<p>Family building grants up to $10,000. Focused on helping those who cannot afford treatment.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>The Samfund</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.thesamfund.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">thesamfund.org</a></p>
			<p>Financial assistance for young adult cancer survivors, including fertility preservation.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>Fertility Within Reach</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.fertilitywithinreach.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">fertilitywithinreach.org</a></p>
			<p>Fertility treatment grants and discounted IVF programs.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>Pay It Forward Fertility Foundation</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.payitforwardfertility.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">payitforwardfertility.org</a></p>
			<p>IVF grants for couples struggling to build their families.</p>
		</div>

		<h3>Medication Assistance</h3>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>EMD Serono Compassionate Care</h3>
			<p>Discounts on Gonal-F and other medications for qualifying patients.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>Ferring Heart to Heart</h3>
			<p>Free fertility medications for qualifying patients.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>ReUnite Rx</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.reuniterx.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">reuniterx.com</a></p>
			<p>Discounted fertility medications.</p>
		</div>

		<h3>Fertility Loans and Financing</h3>

		<ul>
			<li><strong>Future Family</strong> - Fertility-specific loans and payment plans</li>
			<li><strong>Prosper Healthcare Lending</strong> - Medical financing</li>
			<li><strong>CapexMD</strong> - Fertility financing</li>
			<li><strong>LendingClub</strong> - Personal loans</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Support Groups</h2>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>RESOLVE Support Groups</h3>
			<p><a href="https://resolve.org/support/support-groups/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">resolve.org/support</a></p>
			<p>In-person and online support groups across the US, led by trained volunteers.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>Fertility Network</h3>
			<p>Online communities on Reddit (r/infertility, r/IVF), Facebook groups, and other platforms.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>Therapy and Counseling</h3>
			<p>Many fertility clinics have counselors on staff. Look for therapists who specialize in infertility through ASRM's mental health professional group.</p>
		</div>

		<h2>Educational Resources</h2>

		<h3>Websites</h3>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>FertilityIQ</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.fertilityiq.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">fertilityiq.com</a></p>
			<p>In-depth courses on fertility treatments, doctor reviews, and clinic comparisons.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>ASRM Patient Fact Sheets</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.reproductivefacts.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">reproductivefacts.org</a></p>
			<p>Peer-reviewed fact sheets on fertility topics from the American Society for Reproductive Medicine.</p>
		</div>

		<h3>Books</h3>

		<ul>
			<li><strong>"The Infertility Survival Handbook"</strong> by Elizabeth Swire Falker</li>
			<li><strong>"It Starts with the Egg"</strong> by Rebecca Fett - Research on improving egg quality</li>
			<li><strong>"The Whole Life Fertility Plan"</strong> by Kyra Phillips and Dr. Jamie Grifo</li>
			<li><strong>"Navigating the Land of IF"</strong> by Melissa Ford</li>
		</ul>

		<h3>Podcasts</h3>

		<ul>
			<li><strong>Beat Infertility</strong></li>
			<li><strong>The Fertility Podcast</strong></li>
			<li><strong>Big Fat Negative</strong></li>
			<li><strong>The Egg Whisperer Show</strong></li>
		</ul>

		<h2>LGBTQ+ Family Building</h2>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>Family Equality</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.familyequality.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">familyequality.org</a></p>
			<p>Resources for LGBTQ+ parents and those looking to start families.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>Path2Parenthood</h3>
			<p>LGBTQ+ family building resources and support.</p>
		</div>

		<h2>Donor Conception</h2>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>Donor Sibling Registry</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.donorsiblingregistry.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">donorsiblingregistry.com</a></p>
			<p>Connect donor-conceived people with half-siblings and donors. Resources on disclosure.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>We Are Donor Conceived</h3>
			<p>Organization run by donor-conceived adults with resources for families.</p>
		</div>

		<h2>Gestational Surrogacy</h2>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>American Academy of Assisted Reproductive Technology Attorneys</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.aaartaattorneys.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">aaartaattorneys.org</a></p>
			<p>Find lawyers specializing in reproductive law for surrogacy contracts.</p>
		</div>

		<h2>Pregnancy Loss Support</h2>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>Share Pregnancy & Infant Loss Support</h3>
			<p><a href="https://nationalshare.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">nationalshare.org</a></p>
			<p>Support for those who have experienced pregnancy loss, stillbirth, or infant death.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>The Compassionate Friends</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.compassionatefriends.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">compassionatefriends.org</a></p>
			<p>Support for families grieving the death of a child.</p>
		</div>

		<h2>Alternative Paths to Parenthood</h2>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>AdoptUSKids</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.adoptuskids.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">adoptuskids.org</a></p>
			<p>National resource for adoption from foster care.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>Embryo Adoption Awareness Center</h3>
			<p><a href="https://www.embryoadoption.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">embryoadoption.org</a></p>
			<p>Information on embryo donation and adoption.</p>
		</div>

		<h2>Advocacy</h2>

		<div class="card">
			<h3>RESOLVE Advocacy</h3>
			<p><a href="https://resolve.org/what-we-do/advocacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">resolve.org/advocacy</a></p>
			<p>Get involved in advocating for fertility insurance coverage and patients' rights.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="info-box">
			<strong>Insurance Advocacy:</strong> If your insurance denies coverage, RESOLVE offers resources on appeals and advocacy. Many denials can be overturned with proper documentation and appeal.
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-header {
		background: #edf2f7;
		padding: 3rem 0;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.page-header h1 {
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
	}

	.page-header p {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--color-text-light);
		font-size: 1.125rem;
	}

	.card h3 {
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.card p:first-of-type {
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}
</style>
